import React, { Component } from 'react'

export default class Form extends Component {
    render() {
        return (
            <form>
                <label>Date: </label>
                <input name="date" type="date" />
                <label>Unrealistic Thought: </label>
                <textarea rows="1" className="unrealistic-thought" name="unrealistic-thought" type="description" />
                <fieldset>
                    <label>Congnitive Distortions: </label>
                    <input className="checkbox" type="checkbox" name="cognitive-distortions" value="All or Nothing Thinking" />All or Nothing Thinking
                    <input className="checkbox" type="checkbox" name="cognitive-distortions" value="Overgeneralization" />Overgeneralization
                    <input className="checkbox" type="checkbox" name="cognitive-distortions" value="Mental Filter" />Mental Filter
                    <input className="checkbox" type="checkbox" name="cognitive-distortions" value="Discounting the Positives" />Discounting the Positives
                    <input className="checkbox" type="checkbox" name="cognitive-distortions" value="Jumping to Conclusions - Mind Reading" />Jumping to Conclusions - Mind Reading
                    <input className="checkbox" type="checkbox" name="cognitive-distortions" value="Jumping to Conclusions - Fortune Telling" />Jumping to Conclusions - Fortune Telling
                    <input className="checkbox" type="checkbox" name="cognitive-distortions" value="Magnification/Minimazation" />Magnification/Minimization
                    <input className="checkbox" type="checkbox" name="cognitive-distortions" value="Emotional Reasoning" />Emotional Reasoning
                    <input className="checkbox" type="checkbox" name="cognitive-distortions" value="Should Statement" />"Should" Statement
                    <input className="checkbox" type="checkbox" name="cognitive-distortions" value="Labeling" />Labeling
                    <input className="checkbox" type="checkbox" name="cognitive-distortions" value="Personalization and Blame" />Personalization and Blame
                </fieldset>
                <label>Realistic Reframe: </label>
                <input className="realistic-reframe" name="realistic-reframe" type="text" />
                <button type="submit" >Publish to Journal</button>
            </form>
        );
    }
}
